title: Mutalip Alibekov
text:
Mutalip Omarovich Alibekov (; born 18 June 1997) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Makhachkala">Dynamo Makhachkala</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut for the main squad of <a href="PFC%20CSKA%20Moscow">PFC CSKA Moscow</a> in the <a href="Russian%20Cup%20%28football%29">Russian Cup</a> game against <a href="FC%20Yenisey%20Krasnoyarsk">FC Yenisey Krasnoyarsk</a> on 21 September 2016.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Khimki">FC Khimki</a> on 16 September 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Tambov">FC Tambov</a>.
